{"ts":1778502849656,"jobId":"f7fd6a53-c747-4e1b-9fed-f32f2d956850","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"I understand what you're asking. Let me think through this systematically.\n\n**What I've accomplished so far:**\n- ✅ Completed UTR availability monitoring (cron job)\n- ✅ Audited all projects for uncommitted changes\n- ✅ Cleaned up and pushed two projects (media-automation, email-automation-v2)\n- ✅ Spawned Opus subagent to review todo-dashboard\n- ✅ Verified infrastructure health (email-automation deployment healthy, media automation CronJobs running)\n- ✅ Created today's memory file\n\n**What I'm waiting for:**\n- Subagent to complete todo-dashboard review (will auto-announce)\n\n**What I should be thinking about:**\n\nI've been reactive — responding to uncommitted changes and infrastructure checks. But the bigger question is: **What would be most valuable for Dj right now?**\n\nLooking at my memory and context:\n1. **Email automation system** is deployed and running well (all services healthy)\n2. **Media automation** is running successfully (CronJobs completing)\n3. **Projects are clean** except for the feature work the subagent is handling\n4. **Infrastructure is stable**\n\nBut I notice something: I haven't actually engaged with any of the *active work* — the features being built, the systems being developed. I've just been doing maintenance and cleanup.\n\n**What I should probably do:**\n\nRather than just waiting for the subagent, I should think about:\n- What's the current state of the email automation feature work?\n- What's the status of the todo-dashboard email rules feature?\n- Are there any blocking issues or technical debt I should be aware of?\n- What's the next priority after these changes are committed?\n\nI'm ready to handle the subagent results when they come in. But I should also be thinking strategically about what comes next and what would be most valuable for you.\n\nShould I wait for the subagent to complete, or is there something else you'd like me to focus on?","delivered":false,"deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"e77cb05f-ee33-484c-b844-8ee9dad44cff","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:f7fd6a53-c747-4e1b-9fed-f32f2d956850:run:e77cb05f-ee33-484c-b844-8ee9dad44cff","runAtMs":1778502600038,"durationMs":249593,"nextRunAtMs":1778504400000,"model":"claude-haiku-4.5","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":720393,"output_tokens":13554,"total_tokens":40648}}
