edule it no more frequently than every 10-15 minutes to avoid overlap.\n\n## 🚨 Alert Messages\n- **When available:** `🚨 *Ubiquiti Travel Router is AVAILABLE!* Check…","delivered":false,"deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"97f28cda-b6b9-443e-8a17-61165671e442","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:f7fd6a53-c747-4e1b-9fed-f32f2d956850:run:97f28cda-b6b9-443e-8a17-61165671e442","runAtMs":1778644800020,"durationMs":666387,"nextRunAtMs":1778646600000,"model":"deepseek-3.2","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":309263,"output_tokens":14867,"total_tokens":30709}}
