{"ts":1778663210192,"jobId":"f7fd6a53-c747-4e1b-9fed-f32f2d956850","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"I've successfully executed the Ubiquiti Travel Router availability monitor script. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n## Script Execution Summary\n\n**1. Fetched Product Page**\n- Ran: `curl -s 'https://store.ui.com/us/en/category/wifi-special-devices/products/utr' > /tmp/utr_page.html`\n- File size: 315KB, 549 lines - valid HTML content\n\n**2. Checked Availability Status**\n- Searched for \"Sold Out\": **FOUND** (1 occurrence)\n- Searched for \"Add to Cart\": **NOT FOUND** (0 occurrences)\n- Case-insensitive checks confirmed: \"sold out\" present, \"add to cart\" absent\n\n**3. Read Current State**\n- State file: `/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/utr_state.json`\n- Previous status: `\"sold_out\"`\n- Last checked: `\"2026-05-13T08:36:47Z\"`\n\n**4. Determined Current Status**\n- Current availability: **SOLD OUT** (based on \"Sold Out\" text in HTML)\n- Previous status: **sold_out** (from state file)\n- **Status change**: **NO CHANGE** (product was sold out and remains sold out)\n\n**5. Executed Script Logic**\nAccording to the script's decision tree:\n- ✅ Found \"Sold Out\" → product is SOLD OUT\n- ❌ Did not find \"Add to Cart\" → not available\n- 🔄 Status unchanged (sold_out → sold_out)\n- 📝 Action: Update timestamp only, exit silently\n\n**6. Updated State File**\n- New timestamp: `\"2026-05-13T09:00:00Z\"` (current time from user message)\n- Updated file: `/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/utr_state.json`\n- New content:\n```json\n{\n  \"last_status\": \"sold_out\",\n  \"last_checked\": \"2026-05-13T09:00:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n**7. No Alert Sent**\n- Status unchanged, so no Telegram alert was triggered\n- Script executed as designed: silent exit when no status change\n\n## Verification\n- ✅ Curl command succeeded (file has content)\n- ✅ Availability check performed correctly\n- ✅ State file read/write successful\n- ✅ Script logic followed exactly as specified\n- ✅ Timestamp updated to current time\n\nThe Ubiquiti Travel Router remains sold out. The monitoring script ran successfully and updated the last checked timestamp without sending any aler…","delivered":false,"deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"5ef9a854-7d57-407c-83f4-2861ba996fc8","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:f7fd6a53-c747-4e1b-9fed-f32f2d956850:run:5ef9a854-7d57-407c-83f4-2861ba996fc8","runAtMs":1778662800128,"durationMs":410021,"nextRunAtMs":1778664600000,"model":"deepseek-3.2","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":577322,"output_tokens":8343,"total_tokens":93024}}
