{"ts":1778875449843,"jobId":"f7fd6a53-c747-4e1b-9fed-f32f2d956850","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"I've completed the Ubiquiti Travel Router availability monitoring task. Here's what I executed:\n\n## Task Execution Summary\n\n**1. Fetched product page**: Successfully retrieved the current product page using curl\n**2. Analyzed availability**: Found \"Sold Out\" in the HTML (no \"Add to Cart\" present)\n**3. Current status**: `sold_out` - product is out of stock\n**4. Previous status**: `sold_out` (from state file, last checked: 2026-05-15T19:04:57+00:00)\n**5. Status change**: None - product remains sold out\n**6. State file updated**: Updated timestamp to 2026-05-15T20:02:42+00:00 while maintaining `sold_out` status\n**7. Telegram alert**: Not sent (status unchanged, per monitoring logic)\n\n## Technical Details\n- **HTML analysis**: Used grep to search for \"Sold Out\" and \"Add to Cart\" strings\n- **Status determination**: Product is SOLD OUT based on presence of \"Sold Out\" text\n- **State management**: Maintained in `/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/utr_state.json`\n- **Temporary file**: Created at `/tmp/utr_page.html` (will be cleaned up by system)\n\nThe monitoring logic is now ready to be scheduled as a cron job. When the product status changes (from sold_out to available or vice versa), it will automatically send a Telegram alert to chat ID 8623402151 using the TELEGRAM_TOKEN environment variable.","delivered":false,"deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"ffd5d13b-9e48-44f6-8f57-87ca59a02103","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:f7fd6a53-c747-4e1b-9fed-f32f2d956850:run:ffd5d13b-9e48-44f6-8f57-87ca59a02103","runAtMs":1778875200024,"durationMs":249790,"nextRunAtMs":1778877000000,"model":"deepseek-3.2","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":258456,"output_tokens":7873,"total_tokens":53782}}
{"ts":1778877274052,"jobId":"f7fd6a53-c747-4e1b-9fed-f32f2d956850","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"I've successfully executed the Ubiquiti Travel Router availability monitoring task. Here's a complete summary of what was done:\n\n## Task Execution Summary\n\n### **1. Initial State Check**\n- Read state file: `/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/utr_state.json`\n- Previous status: `sold_out` (last checked: 2026-05-15T20:02:42+00:00)\n\n### **2. Product Page Fetch**\n- Successfully fetched product page using: `curl -s 'https://store.ui.com/us/en/category/wifi-special-devices/products/utr'`\n- Saved to: `/tmp/utr_page.html`\n\n### **3. Availability Analysis**\n- **\"Sold Out\" check**: ✅ FOUND in HTML (case-insensitive grep)\n- **\"Add to Cart\" check**: ❌ NOT FOUND in HTML (case-insensitive grep)\n- **Determined status**: `sold_out` (product is sold out)\n\n### **4. Status Comparison**\n- Previous status: `sold_out`\n- Current status: `sold_out`\n- **Result**: No change in status\n\n### **5. State Update**\n- Updated timestamp to current time: `2026-05-15T20:30:00+00:00`\n- Status remains: `sold_out`\n- No Telegram alert required (status unchanged)\n\n### **6. Cleanup**\n- Removed temporary file: `/tmp/utr_page.html`\n\n## Key Observations\n\n1. **Product Availability**: The Ubiquiti Travel Router (UTR) is currently sold out on the US store.\n2. **Monitoring Logic**: The string matching approach worked correctly:\n   - Found \"Sold Out\" in the HTML (appears as `<div class=\"sc-1x3sjmh-0 cfWhQA\"> Sold Out</div>`)\n   - Did not find \"Add to Cart\" anywhere in the page\n3. **Alert Status**: No alert was sent since the status didn't change from the previous check.\n\n## State File Verification\nThe updated state file now contains:\n```json\n{\n  \"last_status\": \"sold_out\",\n  \"last_checked\": \"2026-05-15T20:30:00+00:00\"\n}\n```\n\nThe monitoring task has been completed successfully. The cron job would exit silently (as per instructions) since the status remained unchanged. The next run will check again and send a Telegram alert only if the status changes to \"available\".","delivered":false,"deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"7fe03e40-5549-4a82-aef7-74cccd397cfd","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:f7fd6a53-c747-4e1b-9fed-f32f2d956850:run:7fe03e40-5549-4a82-aef7-74cccd397cfd","runAtMs":1778877000009,"durationMs":274023,"nextRunAtMs":1778878800000,"model":"deepseek-3.2","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":480348,"output_tokens":6800,"total_tokens":85505}}
