{"ts":1778889785961,"jobId":"f7fd6a53-c747-4e1b-9fed-f32f2d956850","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"I've successfully executed the Ubiquiti Travel Router availability check. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n## Ubiquiti Travel Router Availability Check - Completed\n\n**Current Status**: Sold Out\n**Previous Status**: Sold Out (from 2026-05-15T23:30:00+00:00)\n**Status Change**: None - product remains sold out\n\n### Steps Executed:\n1. ✅ Read existing state file - found last status was \"sold_out\"\n2. ✅ Fetched product page from Ubiquiti store using curl\n3. ✅ Checked page for \"Sold Out\" - found (product is sold out)\n4. ✅ Checked page for \"Add to Cart\" - not found\n5. ✅ Compared current status with previous status - no change\n6. ✅ Updated state file timestamp to 2026-05-16T00:02:00+00:00\n7. ✅ No Telegram alert sent (status unchanged)\n\n### State File Updated:\n```json\n{\n  \"last_status\": \"sold_out\",\n  \"last_checked\": \"2026-05-16T00:02:00+00:00\"\n}\n```\n\nThe monitoring script has been executed successfully. The Ubiquiti Travel Router remains out of stock. If the status changes to \"available\" in a future check, the script will send a Telegram alert to notify you.","delivered":false,"deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"444693cd-4c76-4c70-9fd6-899e35964462","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:f7fd6a53-c747-4e1b-9fed-f32f2d956850:run:444693cd-4c76-4c70-9fd6-899e35964462","runAtMs":1778889600011,"durationMs":185943,"nextRunAtMs":1778891400000,"model":"deepseek-3.2","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":224502,"output_tokens":3705,"total_tokens":48725}}
