top rate limit errors)\n2. **Create a new cron job** with a simpler configuration\n\n**New cron job configuration:**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"utr-simple-monitor\",\n  \"schedule\": {\n  …","deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"ea86e44b-3ed6-4293-a61d-0f671f4eea64","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:f7fd6a53-c747-4e1b-9fed-f32f2d956850:run:ea86e44b-3ed6-4293-a61d-0f671f4eea64","runAtMs":1779530451570,"durationMs":298938,"nextRunAtMs":1779532200000,"model":"deepseek-3.2","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":484940,"output_tokens":6436,"total_tokens":81290}}
